import React from 'react' import './css/BusLogs.css' function BusLogs ({ buses, dates, sendDates }) { return (

{buses[0].from.toUpperCase()}

{buses[0].to.toUpperCase()}

{dates.day}, {dates.date} {dates.month}

{buses[0].time}

{buses[0].remaining} seats available

{buses[0].totalSeats} total seates.

) } export default BusLogs
